## ğŸ¯ Quick Start

### 1. Start the Backend

```bash
cd elliott-wave-trading-bot
python src/web_backend.py
```

The server will start on `http://localhost:5000`

### 2. Open the Dashboard

Open your browser and navigate to:

```
http://localhost:5000/dashboard
```

### 3. First-Time Setup

1. **Check Data Pipeline** (Tab 1)
   - Verify TwelveData API is healthy
   - Check symbol data status
   - Refresh stale data if needed

2. **Run Quality Check** (Tab 3)
   - Click "Run Quality Check"
   - Ensure all symbols have 70+ quality score
   - Review any issues found

3. **Run Signal Scan** (Tab 4)
   - Click "Run Signal Scan"
   - Enable "Use Claude AI" for enhanced analysis (optional)
   - Review qualified signals (score â‰¥75)

