## ğŸ”§ Troubleshooting

### Dashboard Won't Load
```bash
# Check if server is running
curl http://localhost:5000/api/health

# Restart server
python src/web_backend.py
```

### API Errors
```
Error: "No data available for EUR/USD"
â†’ Solution: Go to Tab 1, click "Refresh All Data"

Error: "Rate limit exceeded"
â†’ Solution: Wait for daily reset, check Tab 1 for call count

Error: "TWELVEDATA_API_KEY not found"
â†’ Solution: Set environment variable (see TWELVE_DATA_SETUP.md)
```

### Slow Performance
```
1. Check rate limit health (Tab 1)
   - If < 40%, reduce scan frequency

2. Clear cache and refresh
   - Tab 1 â†’ "Refresh All Data"

3. Reduce validation frequency
   - Tab 5 â†’ Increase min_score or reduce max_validations
```

### Quality Issues
```
If quality < 70:
1. Tab 3 â†’ "Run Quality Check"
2. Review issues in matrix
3. Tab 1 â†’ Refresh affected symbols
4. Tab 3 â†’ Re-check quality
```

