## ğŸš€ API Endpoints Reference

### TwelveData Monitoring
```
GET  /api/twelvedata/status     â†’ API health & metrics
GET  /api/twelvedata/symbols    â†’ Per-symbol status
POST /api/twelvedata/refresh    â†’ Force refresh symbols
```

### Data Quality
```
POST /api/quality/assess   â†’ Assess single symbol (0-100 score)
GET  /api/quality/system   â†’ System-wide quality report
GET  /api/quality/startup  â†’ Quick startup validation
```

### Timeframe Engine
```
GET  /api/timeframes/available   â†’ Valid timeframes from 5m base
POST /api/timeframes/calculate   â†’ Calculate custom timeframe
POST /api/timeframes/resample    â†’ Resample to target timeframe
GET  /api/timeframes/recommend   â†’ Get strategy recommendations
```

### Signals
```
POST /api/scan              â†’ Run market scan
POST /api/analyze/<symbol>  â†’ Analyze specific signal with Claude
GET  /api/performance       â†’ Get trading performance
POST /api/cache/clear       â†’ Clear cache
```

